Mistake: Not listening
Problem: Customer feels ignored
Fix: Practice active listening

Mistake: Blaming others
Problem: Reduces trust
Fix: Take ownership, or guide them to the right help

Mistake: Making unrealistic promises
Problem: Breaks trust
